{"tid":210184,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟男人係咪一世都忘記唔到一個錯過咗嘅女人","createTime":"2017-04-20T17:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T14:07:03.000Z","uid":78960,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41e4f9216483437fb629f35cd05389073faedbd4","tid":210184,"uid":78960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"曾經有個女人好了解我 佢對我有恩 係我最低潮嘅日子扶番起我 為我做咗好多野 但最後因為已經踩過界 所以無疾而終 到離開前一刻都對我好好<br />\n究竟係咪一世都會係一個遺憾 就算我將來有另一半都忘記唔到佢？"},{"pid":"a9ed1f8fa1a02e747b2d714675dd4d1bee2e11ea","tid":210184,"uid":22199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"係 身同感受"},{"pid":"0722b22765e6bcfb109bdb585e550778bc2504a3","tid":210184,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"是的（掛）"},{"pid":"8b2fd18490d0670f0540e9bf85847b37c52ad1ad","tid":210184,"uid":77909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:13:11.000Z","msg":"留住最美麗既回憶，甘心唔忘記佢"},{"pid":"c1399d3307c5810ebdbd9280bf8947787f77f0fb","tid":210184,"uid":20985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:15:52.000Z","msg":"我仲後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a13f71c1ad7fd76ba9fb73acec0dd9ae7e2cce6","tid":210184,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05da6a37096f76838d7f5eef37b749390711eec","tid":210184,"uid":103285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"係！有時都諗返"},{"pid":"a49f8326ef3f4e5bf1ecca78b79b783becf5378e","tid":210184,"uid":20696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T18:47:11.000Z","msg":"得唔到嘅永遠係最好<br />\n失去嘅永遠最難忘記<br />\n遺憾、錯過就最深刻<br />\n人性就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我覺得有時係你太死攬住唔放<br />\n潛意識美化左呢段回憶，加上一齊唔到睇唔到任何唔好嘅地方，永遠淨係記得佢有幾好。先會有所謂忘記唔到，你根本無諗過忘記「咁美好」嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但咁樣只會令你睇唔到身邊嘅人嘅好，然後再一次錯過，再一次懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819ad08cb710df867b789eae7da36f89cb2c6c13","tid":210184,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"係 幾年了"},{"pid":"b05303a940695daffaa03aefacdbe48a49403c18","tid":210184,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T19:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ee9ec967d77b8a7fa2946c7295879250a7d06f","tid":210184,"uid":59432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T19:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c624e998d94e664d5d9dc264aae83bfee26d0615","tid":210184,"uid":14392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"我都好後悔 ，個女仔有男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c40733c125fb89e215b402fb49b87de6ebd3d5","tid":210184,"uid":51758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"745be92819dc73f8f6989a8b2fee3f4a7ce85dd5","tid":210184,"uid":64178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:24:03.000Z","msg":"臭雞一個<br />\n忘記佢啦"},{"pid":"a23a2eb06b71ebde1ed819a777e9dad29c2e8059","tid":210184,"uid":84123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"幻想中既永遠最美好<br />\n呢種幻想只會成為現在感情既絆腳石<br />\n所以都係放下啦"},{"pid":"7cfcbeddb0ff76eb6599176fd3667f99deb23ca8","tid":210184,"uid":7833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好後悔 ，個女仔有男朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣... 心情好矛盾<br />\n又為佢搵到自己既幸福開心<br />\n但又希望果個男人係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e02998fe210f77728921c98bb1e08ef09dbe62","tid":210184,"uid":104895,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"放低啦 客觀啲諗下你地一齊既時候開唔開心 佢對你係米認真 愛唔愛你 對你好唔好先 有時挽回唔倒係會令你唔甘心 先會加強左以為自己好愛佢無左佢唔得既心態<br />\n冷靜啲諗就算比你同佢一齊番 你地真係夾咩 佢會真心對你好 愛你咩<br />\n有時"},{"pid":"690a6b2d2095e0f27eaac3c7eaeabeb5605c8a26","tid":210184,"uid":104895,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放低啦 客觀啲諗下你地一齊既時候開唔開心 佢對你係米認真 愛唔愛你 對你好唔好先 有時挽回唔倒係會令你唔甘心 先會加強左以為自己好愛佢無左佢唔得既心態<br />\n冷靜啲諗就算比你同佢一齊番 你地真係夾咩 佢會真心對你好 愛你咩<br />\n有時過去左就係過去左 好好珍惜同留意依家身邊真心對你好 愛你既人好過啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"49cfb7764c0f2c1b29234d5ecfc5c3cd1e9935c8","tid":210184,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"得不到永遠是最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0cd07043fe3ce59e4b29375dd2d5476480cefd","tid":210184,"uid":42072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經有個女人好了解我 佢對我有恩 係我最低潮嘅日子扶番起我 為我做咗好多野 但最後因為已經踩過界 所以無疾而終 到離開前一刻都對我好好<br />\n究竟係咪一世都會係一個遺憾 就算我將來有另一半都忘記唔到佢？</blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"879cb9306e4ad6b515d2967525d695d2975d9c4f","tid":210184,"uid":47512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ed6b3611d8c887f1fc0d0171adc7ad5141b9b48","tid":210184,"uid":62859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"唉 ex就係忘記