ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a6b3b1cfa8013f7c52d2d53d383eeced5154d8","tid":210184,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係, 我曾經錯過左3個, 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果可以重來一次, 我一定會好好把握機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好後悔 應該開始時冇勇氣去做"},{"pid":"02704f23f4c9275f9e74be4a48882124b5d4a8c6","tid":210184,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係, 我曾經錯過左3個, 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果可以重來一次, 我一定會好好把握機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好後悔 應該開始時冇勇氣去做</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我都係。。。<br />\n明明大家鐘意大家 如果我可以遲多少少識佢就好了"},{"pid":"2471a48d30a52ed035706e676e7cf934a2e8a10c","tid":210184,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係, 我曾經錯過左3個, 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果可以重來一次, 我一定會好好把握機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好後悔 應該開始時冇勇氣去做</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我都係。。。<br />\n明明大家鐘意大家 如果我可以遲多少少識佢就好了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係相反 如果我可以早多少少識佢就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b814d246206804e4862cd7b31cd77fa4308b37","tid":210184,"uid":78960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483a3cbb871fd45ec365c96cb15390e10cef50c0","tid":210184,"uid":88385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"有時諗返起 都好後悔<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"9b5e5521c30c1fa6839e1ada2bc9b63346798a77","tid":210184,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"係，中學果時為左打機而錯過左一個人（on9)，而呢個人亦都好可能係唯一一個鍾意過我既人。<br />\n<br />\n巴打/絲打們記住如果有人同你地表明心意或者想追人，就唔好唔嗲唔吊，呢個世界係無如果架。<br />\n<br />\n有人向你表白，唔該比返個回應人地。<br />\n想追人既，就唔好思思縮縮，行動最實際（約睇戲，食飯，乜柒都好）好過左諗右諗而唔踏出第一步。<br />\n<br />\n當日我就係因為置之不理呢個向我表白既人搞到直到而家我都係忘記唔到佢足足有7年⋯<br />\n中學時代真係最有機會拍拖既一段時間，大家要好好珍惜<br />\n頭盔：男 中六畢業  無女性朋友 理想主義者的鳩up<br />\n最後祝天下有情人終成眷屬"},{"pid":"3f77eb1d369c99cdda38c84e5b27b1740e047f5a","tid":210184,"uid":69488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"當時誰對你凝望過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0deb3d84133f879a40fdafd437d1ef2b065284e2","tid":210184,"uid":88385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T18:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時誰對你凝望過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個名好聽落去好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4941829455bbb68962376de03e79392276567db1","tid":210184,"uid":84133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T18:30:37.000Z","msg":"係 我知道我好愛佢 宜家係以後都係<br />\n不過果陣愛已經唔係想得到佢<br />\n只係希望佢可以好好地 幸福咁生活落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咁諗 每個男人心目中都會有一個紫霞仙子"},{"pid":"94c1292dbe94945886bec9a010b25117de53daef","tid":210184,"uid":16156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T18:58:07.000Z","msg":"Ys"},{"pid":"3db3442724c8ea71e73a62dc07ffcbf53c79568b","tid":210184,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:10:17.000Z","msg":"是的"},{"pid":"f6389802d3b82420a64dd69fd72ec2e9e7ad280a","tid":210184,"uid":14392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:14:21.000Z","msg":"最心痛是愛得太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1baee94ce243fa422e5dc27f6913b154fe4770a2","tid":210184,"uid":104232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:29:33.000Z","msg":"我好鐘意我前度 <br />\n做錯好多事 衰好多衝動<br />\n對不起 我還喜歡你"},{"pid":"94f591a1f8a6648101b47410616363b0e0cf6846","tid":210184,"uid":62981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T19:31:23.000Z","msg":"係 8年了<br />\n後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2977de2621106bf52c108e51405b25fd45be7f","tid":210184,"uid":75004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好鐘意我前度 <br />\n做錯好多事 衰好多衝動<br />\n對不起 我還喜歡你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢令我改變好多 做返好自已。"},{"pid":"79ed5558d078a764e37bf7e67fa59dc35b3474d0","tid":210184,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T20:43:59.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心入面都有一個放唔低既女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係會好支持我<br />\n但係我就真係做乜都吸引唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢件事係令我幾自卑<br />\n<br />\n呢兩三年都係度諗<br />\n好彩無一齊 因為都深知長久唔到 可能失去更多<br />\n但係其實一切都係自我安慰<br />\n<br />\n如果同佢一齊<br />\n我會比我最好既野佢 比哂我成個人<br />\n盡力去愛佢<br />\n<br />\n得不到 先有遺憾 先至可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}